show trace
c and c++

show function name:
from app:
printf("%s():\n", __FUNCTION__);
 
from linux driver:
printk("%s():\n", __FUNCTION__);
 
show file name:
from app:
 printf("file %s\n", __FILE__);
 
from linux driver:
 printk("file %s\n", __FILE__);
 
show line number:
from app:
printf("line %d\n", __LINE__);
 
from linux driver:
printk("line %d\n", __LINE__);